channel.title: ReneScape Need Devo team!
channel.description:
Hello there, This is my server ReneScape. I'm still working on it but ill show off here what i've got so far. I'm not such a good coder, I just try my best. If you would like to flame me, have a go, if it makes you feel alright.
Exp rate is x350 No pure or master commands. Because i think they take away the fun of the server.
Pictures! [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/1-ZsUyK.bmp[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/2-mPSqH.bmp[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/3-CmmZI.bmp[/img] [img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/4-1wkBN.bmp[/img]
Tell me what you think!
If you would like to have a look you can download the client here: *
Sincerely,
Rene!
Update: Added thieving!
[img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/thieving-olZn8.png[/img]
Feeling good :D
New updates!
[img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/cooking-n888C.png[/img]
[img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/firemaking-CZJhI.png[/img]
[img]http://www.imagenerd.com/uploads/woodcutting-4pA7G.png[/img]
yo, So yeah, i need a devo team, Look up there for what i already have!
You can apply for any function You would like. The things i espescially need is a Client Coder.
Form: What function are you applying for? What's your age? How long is your experience? Why do you want to take this function? How much are you online? Are you ownage?
